{"tid":1344003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩交通逼人罷工 切記！","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T20:35:40.000Z","uid":252262,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"005fdee528b4e8f99d145704d966ddc35ed39755","tid":1344003,"uid":252262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:09:16.000Z","msg":"一定要同市民講清楚行動背後嘅動機同目的，而唔係齋搞交通咩都唔講，因為香港人對冇得返工係最反感，而且到時定有傳媒在場，不合作運動除咗直接阻人返工之外，亦可以靠傳媒向市民解釋我地唔係為玩而搞交通，務求得到市民理解同體諒，因為好多人只係睇到表面（阻地鐵=搞亂社會=搞破壞），必須要儘量攞光環，唔好俾位紅媒同藍絲入！<br />\n<br />\n而宣傳可以air drop圖，播錄音/片，派傳單，甚至係整連儂列車，到時再諗！"},{"pid":"380d3ca291953a47ab723aed14d0a4f3e0684a92","tid":1344003,"uid":252262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"睡前一推 大家加油"},{"pid":"250bc6260ce6bc07218f6d8d5a5a0e4abaab48b2","tid":1344003,"uid":252262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:23:19.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6679e4960f851ac2144fcbd1bed63b0e9da64431","tid":1344003,"uid":252262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:28:25.000Z","msg":"好重要！"},{"pid":"f7a852fe80bf1e290176d432f9c1deea0baef80f","tid":1344003,"uid":252262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:30:09.000Z","msg":"Last push"},{"pid":"9df47072f7a38e8c4bfe1cd9c41040f498817df9","tid":1344003,"uid":256281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:34:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30230d7c5d34e3d91d658ea9e19184093f758069","tid":1344003,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:35:40.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好搞呢d呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行車路:<br />\n- 三隧<br />\n- 汀九橋<br />\n- 青馬大橋<br />\n- 港豬澳大橋<br />\n- 港深西部公路<br />\n- 大欖隧道<br />\n- 海安路(青山公路汀九段入荃灣嗰段)<br />\n- 荃灣路<br />\n- 象鼻山路(荃灣來往城門隧道)<br />\n- 大埔公路沙田段<br />\n